title: Remodeled 3+2 Penthouse Condo in a Gated Community
posting_body: ['STUNNING 3+2 PENTHOUSE CONDO JUST UNDER 1100 SQFT; REMODELLED AND MOVE IN READY.', 'PRIVATE/QUIET LOCATION IN THE BACK OF A SECURED COMPLEX WITH 2 CAR COVERED TANDEM PARKING.', 'LARGE BALCONY W/STORAGE ROOM W/GARDEN VIEWS; UPPER LEVEL CORNER UNIT W/HIGH CEILINGS AND NO ONE ABOVE;LIGHT AND BRIGHT W/SKYLIGHTS AND LARGE WINDOWS IN THE LIVING ROOM.', 'CENTRAL A/C AND HEATING W/SMART NEST THERMOSTAT.', 'UPGRADED KITCHEN CABINETS+GRANITE', 'COUNTER TOPS/BAR TOP/BUILT IN MICROWAVE/RECESS LIGHTS,SIDE BY SIDE 25 CF FRIDGE W/ICE MAKER+WATER.', 'REMODELLED BATHS W/MARBLE SLAB COUNTERS/MAPLE WOOD VANITIES & CUSTOM TILE WALL ENCLOSURES W/BUILT IN SHELVES AND SHOWER DOORS.', 'GORGEOUS CUSTOM TILE FLOORS THROUGHOUT.', 'NEW CEILING FANS IN ALL BEDROOM.', 'NEWER CIRCUIT BREAKER, CABLE READY; MASTER BEDROOM', 'W/3', 'CLOSETS + PRIVATE BATH.', 'VERY CLOSE', 'THE LAUNDRY ROOM, POOL AND SPA.', 'EASY ACCESS TO THE 101 FREEWAY, VENTURA BLVD, PLACES OF WORKSHIP, RESTAURANTS AND MORE.', 'RENT INCLUDES WATER & TRASH.', 'UNFURNISHED.', 'Please contact Al for a private showing', 'Keller Williams Realty', 'License# 01872625']
